title: Thunderbolts by Warren Ellis Vol. 2: Caged Angels (Trade Paperback)
description:
Mind over murder! Super-villains drafted into serving as federal marshals, the Thunderbolts specialize in hunting down unlicensed super heroes — but they may be doing their jobs a bit too well. The prisons are full, so Thunderbolts Mountain is serving as a temporary jail while they process all their latest prisoners — some of whom happen to be ruthless psychics bent on destroying the team from within. And since the Thunderbolts include horrific head-cases like Venom, Swordsman, Moonstone and the Green Goblin, a little mental manipulation can be a very dangerous thing. Collecting THUNDERBOLTS #116-121.
144 PGS./Rated T+ …$14.99
ISBN: 978-0-7851-2567-9
